CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 18 reads: "4. The Bell Telephone booth attracted thousands with their informative demonstrations by Jim Fitzsimmons, Terry D'Angelo, Jane Ross, Flossie Felser and Horman Hawk."
TitMainTitle: Men and women, including Jim Fitzsimmons, Terry D'Angelo, Jane Ross, Flossie Felser, and Horman Hawk, gathered in Bell Telephone booth in Syria Mosque for 1957 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair Trade
